</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-bQtKYq czWvgn pf-32_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-33_ pf-text-1"><strong>Federation of Small Businesses (FSB) </strong>- An organisation that offers members a wide range of vital business services, including advice, financial expertise, support, and a powerful voice heard in government.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-35_ pf-text-1"><strong>Compliance</strong> - The process of ensuring that a company meets all legal and regulatory requirements relevant to its operations.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-37_ pf-text-1"><strong>Regulatory compliance </strong>- Adherence to laws, regulations, guidelines, and specifications relevant to business processes.





